Rosetta
========

Yet another localization layer for Rails I18n.

Example
=======

Provides database storage of translations and a more user-friendly missing translation view.

Stores locales, keys (with namespace) for translated strings, and the actual translations in:

i18n_locales
i18n_translated_strings
i18n_translations

respectively.

provides models Locale, TranslatedString, and Translation to manage translations

Provides translated attributes for ActiveRecord models


